Package network.protocol

Contains all enums which define the Strings used by the protocol.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ErrorMessagesEnglish
    Contains all possible error messages send by the Server.
    ProtocolJSONObjectConverter
    A collection of functions for converting protocol JSONObjects to other Objects.
    ProtocolStringConverter
    A collection of functions for converting protocol Strings to other Objects and vice versa.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    Attributes
    Enum of all attributes used in the protocol.
    CheatCodes
    Represents all cheat codes which can be used in the game.
    ClientTypes
    Enum of all protocol strings which can be received by the client.
    ServerTypes
    Enum of all protocol strings which can be received by the Server.
